Package teech.sdk

Class Summary
Assessments Assessments let you manage the assessment process by creating rules that can be used later to evaluate students submissions to assignments.
Assignments Using assignments you can attach materials to modules and register students submissions in order to analyze and track their performance.
Connect  
Enrollment Enrollments allows you to enroll a user in a module and keep track of users enrollments.
Material Materials are designed to shape didactic materials objects.
Module A module it’s a container with a certain number of didactic materials attached to it as assignments.
Query Teech.io REST API let you retrieve items in a very flexible way.
Submission Submissions lets you to assess students based on assignments and evaluate their performance.
Teech  
TeechFile Teech.io cloud storage let you store and retrieve files of size up to 64MB each.
TeechModel  
TeechObject Teech.io REST API is built around JSON encoding of data and a schemaless data structure.
User A user object, like any other object, has a flexible schema but a username and a password are required.
